{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":928,"text":"Why do we cheat?"},{"time":4420,"text":"And why do happy people cheat?"},{"time":8641,"text":"And when we say \"infidelity,\"\nwhat exactly do we mean?"},{"time":14207,"text":"Is it a hookup, a love story,\npaid sex, a chat room,"},{"time":20586,"text":"a massage with a happy ending?"},{"time":24356,"text":"Why do we think that men cheat\nout of boredom and fear of intimacy,"},{"time":29494,"text":"but women cheat out of loneliness\nand hunger for intimacy?"},{"time":35769,"text":"And is an affair always\nthe end of a relationship?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":41294,"text":"For the past 10 years,\nI have traveled the globe"},{"time":44490,"text":"and worked extensively\nwith hundreds of couples"},{"time":47535,"text":"who have been shattered by infidelity."},{"time":50999,"text":"There is one simple act of transgression"},{"time":54641,"text":"that can rob a couple\nof their relationship,"},{"time":59015,"text":"their happiness and their\nvery identity: an affair."},{"time":63903,"text":"And yet, this extremely common\nact is so poorly understood."},{"time":70593,"text":"So this talk is for anyone\nwho has ever loved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77681,"text":"Adultery has existed\nsince marriage was invented,"},{"time":81525,"text":"and so, too, the taboo against it."},{"time":85094,"text":"In fact, infidelity has a tenacity\nthat marriage can only envy,"},{"time":90827,"text":"so much so, that this is\nthe only commandment"},{"time":94289,"text":"that is repeated twice in the Bible:"},{"time":98221,"text":"once for doing it, and once\njust for thinking about it."},{"time":102349,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":104619,"text":"So how do we reconcile\nwhat is universally forbidden,"},{"time":108922,"text":"yet universally practiced?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":113058,"text":"Now, throughout history, men\npractically had a license to cheat"},{"time":118036,"text":"with little consequence,"},{"time":120331,"text":"and supported by a host\nof biological and evolutionary theories"},{"time":124739,"text":"that justified their need to roam,"},{"time":127315,"text":"so the double standard\nis as old as adultery itself."},{"time":132403,"text":"But who knows what's really going on\nunder the sheets there, right?"},{"time":137920,"text":"Because when it comes to sex,"},{"time":139776,"text":"the pressure for men\nis to boast and to exaggerate,"},{"time":143939,"text":"but the pressure for women\nis to hide, minimize and deny,"},{"time":149484,"text":"which isn't surprising when you consider\nthat there are still nine countries"},{"time":153710,"text":"where women can be killed for straying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157825,"text":"Now, monogamy used to be\none person for life."},{"time":162912,"text":"Today, monogamy is one person at a time."},{"time":166268,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":168158,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":172364,"text":"I mean, many of you probably have said,"},{"time":174300,"text":"\"I am monogamous in all my relationships.\""},{"time":177460,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180617,"text":"We used to marry,"},{"time":182260,"text":"and had sex for the first time."},{"time":184614,"text":"But now we marry,"},{"time":186076,"text":"and we stop having sex with others."},{"time":189455,"text":"The fact is that monogamy\nhad nothing to do with love."},{"time":194332,"text":"Men relied on women's fidelity"},{"time":196919,"text":"in order to know whose children these are,"},{"time":199959,"text":"and who gets the cows when I die."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204205,"text":"Now, everyone wants to know"},{"time":206655,"text":"what percentage of people cheat."},{"time":208403,"text":"I've been asked that question\nsince I arrived at this conference."},{"time":211658,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":214260,"text":"It applies to you."},{"time":216466,"text":"But the definition of infidelity\nkeeps on expanding:"},{"time":220959,"text":"sexting, watching porn, staying\nsecretly active on dating apps."},{"time":226332,"text":"So because there is no\nuniversally agreed-upon definition"},{"time":230817,"text":"of what even constitutes an infidelity,"},{"time":233956,"text":"estimates vary widely,\nfrom 26 percent to 75 percent."},{"time":240728,"text":"But on top of it, we are\nwalking contradictions."},{"time":244173,"text":"So 95 percent of us will say\nthat it is terribly wrong"},{"time":247792,"text":"for our partner to lie\nabout having an affair,"},{"time":250969,"text":"but just about the same\namount of us will say"},{"time":253214,"text":"that that's exactly what we\nwould do if we were having one."},{"time":256372,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":259872,"text":"Now, I like this definition\nof an affair --"},{"time":263577,"text":"it brings together the three key elements:"},{"time":267326,"text":"a secretive relationship,\nwhich is the core structure of an affair;"},{"time":273032,"text":"an emotional connection\nto one degree or another;"},{"time":277826,"text":"and a sexual alchemy."},{"time":280355,"text":"And alchemy is the key word here,"},{"time":283337,"text":"because the erotic frisson is such that\nthe kiss that you only imagine giving,"},{"time":290265,"text":"can be as powerful and as enchanting"},{"time":293349,"text":"as hours of actual lovemaking."},{"time":297759,"text":"As Marcel Proust said,"},{"time":299340,"text":"it's our imagination that is responsible\nfor love, not the other person."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305902,"text":"So it's never been easier to cheat,"},{"time":309762,"text":"and it's never been more\ndifficult to keep a secret."},{"time":313999,"text":"And never has infidelity exacted\nsuch a psychological toll."},{"time":319975,"text":"When marriage was an economic enterprise,"},{"time":323342,"text":"infidelity threatened\nour economic security."},{"time":327083,"text":"But now that marriage\nis a romantic arrangement,"},{"time":329959,"text":"infidelity threatens\nour emotional security."},{"time":333779,"text":"Ironically, we used to turn to adultery --"},{"time":338040,"text":"that was the space where\nwe sought pure love."},{"time":341293,"text":"But now that we seek love in marriage,"},{"time":343482,"text":"adultery destroys it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346943,"text":"Now, there are three ways that I think\ninfidelity hurts differently today."},{"time":353800,"text":"We have a romantic ideal\nin which we turn to one person"},{"time":359613,"text":"to fulfill an endless list of needs:"},{"time":362810,"text":"to be my greatest lover, my best friend,"},{"time":366410,"text":"the best parent, my trusted confidant,"},{"time":369563,"text":"my emotional companion,\nmy intellectual equal."},{"time":373625,"text":"And I am it: I'm chosen, I'm unique,"},{"time":377929,"text":"I'm indispensable, I'm irreplaceable,"},{"time":381245,"text":"I'm the one."},{"time":383356,"text":"And infidelity tells me I'm not."},{"time":387308,"text":"It is the ultimate betrayal."},{"time":389999,"text":"Infidelity shatters\nthe grand ambition of love."},{"time":394680,"text":"But if throughout history,\ninfidelity has always been painful,"},{"time":399561,"text":"today it is often traumatic,"},{"time":401919,"text":"because it threatens our sense of self."}]},{"cues":[{"time":405054,"text":"So my patient Fernando, he's plagued."},{"time":407847,"text":"He goes on: \"I thought I knew my life."},{"time":410595,"text":"I thought I knew who you were,\nwho we were as a couple, who I was."},{"time":414801,"text":"Now, I question everything.\""},{"time":417632,"text":"Infidelity -- a violation of trust,\na crisis of identity."},{"time":422819,"text":"\"Can I ever trust you again?\" he asks."},{"time":425148,"text":"\"Can I ever trust anyone again?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":428824,"text":"And this is also what my patient\nHeather is telling me,"},{"time":431905,"text":"when she's talking to me\nabout her story with Nick."},{"time":434532,"text":"Married, two kids."},{"time":435982,"text":"Nick just left on a business trip,"},{"time":438659,"text":"and Heather is playing\non his iPad with the boys,"},{"time":442190,"text":"when she sees a message\nappear on the screen:"},{"time":445127,"text":"\"Can't wait to see you.\""},{"time":447625,"text":"Strange, she thinks,\nwe just saw each other."},{"time":450863,"text":"And then another message:"},{"time":452903,"text":"\"Can't wait to hold you in my arms.\""},{"time":455999,"text":"And Heather realizes"},{"time":458243,"text":"these are not for her."},{"time":460435,"text":"She also tells me\nthat her father had affairs,"},{"time":463812,"text":"but her mother, she found\none little receipt in the pocket,"},{"time":467777,"text":"and a little bit of lipstick\non the collar."},{"time":471221,"text":"Heather, she goes digging,"},{"time":474610,"text":"and she finds hundreds of messages,"},{"time":477673,"text":"and photos exchanged\nand desires expressed."},{"time":481420,"text":"The vivid details\nof Nick's two-year affair"},{"time":484118,"text":"unfold in front of her in real time,"},{"time":487999,"text":"And it made me think:"},{"time":489272,"text":"Affairs in the digital age\nare death by a thousand cuts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495854,"text":"But then we have another paradox\nthat we're dealing with these days."},{"time":499113,"text":"Because of this romantic ideal,"},{"time":501417,"text":"we are relying on our partner's\nfidelity with a unique fervor."},{"time":506999,"text":"But we also have never\nbeen more inclined to stray,"},{"time":510544,"text":"and not because we have new desires today,"},{"time":513255,"text":"but because we live in an era"},{"time":515001,"text":"where we feel that we are\nentitled to pursue our desires,"},{"time":518682,"text":"because this is the culture\nwhere I deserve to be happy."},{"time":523268,"text":"And if we used to divorce\nbecause we were unhappy,"},{"time":527035,"text":"today we divorce\nbecause we could be happier."},{"time":531562,"text":"And if divorce carried all the shame,"},{"time":534847,"text":"today, choosing to stay when you can leave"},{"time":538738,"text":"is the new shame."},{"time":540657,"text":"So Heather, she can't talk to her friends"},{"time":543168,"text":"because she's afraid that they\nwill judge her for still loving Nick,"},{"time":546429,"text":"and everywhere she turns,\nshe gets the same advice:"},{"time":549977,"text":"Leave him. Throw the dog on the curb."},{"time":553744,"text":"And if the situation were reversed,\nNick would be in the same situation."},{"time":559070,"text":"Staying is the new shame."}]},{"cues":[{"time":563395,"text":"So if we can divorce,"},{"time":566359,"text":"why do we still have affairs?"},{"time":569999,"text":"Now, the typical assumption\nis that if someone cheats,"},{"time":574563,"text":"either there's something wrong\nin your relationship or wrong with you."},{"time":579440,"text":"But millions of people\ncan't all be pathological."},{"time":584383,"text":"The logic goes like this: If you\nhave everything you need at home,"},{"time":588291,"text":"then there is no need\nto go looking elsewhere,"},{"time":591715,"text":"assuming that there is such\na thing as a perfect marriage"},{"time":595187,"text":"that will inoculate us against wanderlust."},{"time":599165,"text":"But what if passion\nhas a finite shelf life?"},{"time":603624,"text":"What if there are things\nthat even a good relationship"},{"time":607338,"text":"can never provide?"},{"time":610187,"text":"If even happy people cheat,"},{"time":613202,"text":"what is it about?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":616765,"text":"The vast majority of people\nthat I actually work with"},{"time":619641,"text":"are not at all chronic philanderers."},{"time":622429,"text":"They are often people who are\ndeeply monogamous in their beliefs,"},{"time":626475,"text":"and at least for their partner."},{"time":628865,"text":"But they find themselves in a conflict"},{"time":631501,"text":"between their values and their behavior."},{"time":635572,"text":"They often are people who have\nactually been faithful for decades,"},{"time":639935,"text":"but one day they cross a line"},{"time":642574,"text":"that they never thought they would cross,"},{"time":645047,"text":"and at the risk of losing everything."},{"time":648730,"text":"But for a glimmer of what?"},{"time":651969,"text":"Affairs are an act of betrayal,"},{"time":654609,"text":"and they are also an expression\nof longing and loss."},{"time":658610,"text":"At the heart of an affair,\nyou will often find"},{"time":662528,"text":"a longing and a yearning\nfor an emotional connection,"},{"time":666789,"text":"for novelty, for freedom,\nfor autonomy, for sexual intensity,"},{"time":672559,"text":"a wish to recapture\nlost parts of ourselves"},{"time":676226,"text":"or an attempt to bring back\nvitality in the face of loss and tragedy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":682849,"text":"I'm thinking about\nanother patient of mine, Priya,"},{"time":685766,"text":"who is blissfully married,"},{"time":688382,"text":"loves her husband,"},{"time":689847,"text":"and would never want to hurt the man."},{"time":692713,"text":"But she also tells me"},{"time":694831,"text":"that she's always done\nwhat was expected of her:"},{"time":698005,"text":"good girl, good wife, good mother,"},{"time":701685,"text":"taking care of her immigrant parents."},{"time":704677,"text":"Priya, she fell for the arborist\nwho removed the tree from her yard"},{"time":709214,"text":"after Hurricane Sandy."},{"time":711524,"text":"And with his truck and his tattoos,\nhe's quite the opposite of her."},{"time":717547,"text":"But at 47, Priya's affair is about\nthe adolescence that she never had."},{"time":723753,"text":"And her story highlights for me\nthat when we seek the gaze of another,"},{"time":729030,"text":"it isn't always our partner\nthat we are turning away from,"},{"time":733748,"text":"but the person that\nwe have ourselves become."},{"time":737728,"text":"And it isn't so much that we're\nlooking for another person,"},{"time":741274,"text":"as much as we are\nlooking for another self."}]},{"cues":[{"time":747045,"text":"Now, all over the world,"},{"time":748602,"text":"there is one word that people\nwho have affairs always tell me."},{"time":753030,"text":"They feel alive."},{"time":756046,"text":"And they often will tell me\nstories of recent losses --"},{"time":760286,"text":"of a parent who died,"},{"time":762141,"text":"and a friend that went too soon,"},{"time":764341,"text":"and bad news at the doctor."},{"time":767482,"text":"Death and mortality often live\nin the shadow of an affair,"},{"time":772138,"text":"because they raise these questions."},{"time":774632,"text":"Is this it? Is there more?"},{"time":777901,"text":"Am I going on for another\n25 years like this?"},{"time":781870,"text":"Will I ever feel that thing again?"},{"time":786377,"text":"And it has led me to think\nthat perhaps these questions"},{"time":790788,"text":"are the ones that propel\npeople to cross the line,"},{"time":793947,"text":"and that some affairs are\nan attempt to beat back deadness,"},{"time":797939,"text":"in an antidote to death."}]},{"cues":[{"time":801999,"text":"And contrary to what you may think,"},{"time":804867,"text":"affairs are way less about sex,\nand a lot more about desire:"},{"time":809903,"text":"desire for attention,\ndesire to feel special,"},{"time":813392,"text":"desire to feel important."},{"time":816237,"text":"And the very structure of an affair,"},{"time":819247,"text":"the fact that you can\nnever have your lover,"},{"time":821503,"text":"keeps you wanting."},{"time":822938,"text":"That in itself is a desire machine,"},{"time":825959,"text":"because the incompleteness, the ambiguity,"},{"time":828747,"text":"keeps you wanting\nthat which you can't have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":833641,"text":"Now some of you probably think"},{"time":835177,"text":"that affairs don't happen\nin open relationships,"},{"time":838807,"text":"but they do."},{"time":840432,"text":"First of all, the conversation\nabout monogamy is not the same"},{"time":843562,"text":"as the conversation about infidelity."},{"time":846468,"text":"But the fact is that it seems\nthat even when we have"},{"time":849959,"text":"the freedom to have other sexual partners,"},{"time":852632,"text":"we still seem to be lured\nby the power of the forbidden,"},{"time":856720,"text":"that if we do that which\nwe are not supposed to do,"},{"time":860207,"text":"then we feel like we are really\ndoing what we want to."},{"time":865331,"text":"And I've also told\nquite a few of my patients"},{"time":868935,"text":"that if they could bring\ninto their relationships"},{"time":873536,"text":"one tenth of the boldness,\nthe imagination and the verve"},{"time":877167,"text":"that they put into their affairs,"},{"time":878879,"text":"they probably would never need to see me."},{"time":881148,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":884362,"text":"So how do we heal from an affair?"},{"time":888428,"text":"Desire runs deep."},{"time":890371,"text":"Betrayal runs deep."},{"time":893266,"text":"But it can be healed."},{"time":895999,"text":"And some affairs are death knells"},{"time":898944,"text":"for relationships that were\nalready dying on the vine."},{"time":902753,"text":"But others will jolt us\ninto new possibilities."},{"time":905953,"text":"The fact is, the majority of couples"},{"time":907936,"text":"who have experienced\naffairs stay together."},{"time":910766,"text":"But some of them will merely survive,"},{"time":913399,"text":"and others will actually be able\nto turn a crisis into an opportunity."},{"time":918817,"text":"They'll be able to turn this\ninto a generative experience."},{"time":922484,"text":"And I'm actually thinking even\nmore so for the deceived partner,"},{"time":926222,"text":"who will often say,"},{"time":927558,"text":"\"You think I didn't want more?"},{"time":929365,"text":"But I'm not the one who did it.\""},{"time":931968,"text":"But now that the affair is exposed,"},{"time":934110,"text":"they, too, get to claim more,"},{"time":936244,"text":"and they no longer have\nto uphold the status quo"},{"time":938886,"text":"that may not have been working\nfor them that well, either."}]},{"cues":[{"time":944221,"text":"I've noticed that a lot of couples,"},{"time":947110,"text":"in the immediate aftermath of an affair,"},{"time":949251,"text":"because of this new disorder\nthat may actually lead to a new order,"},{"time":953587,"text":"will have depths of conversations\nwith honesty and openness"},{"time":957169,"text":"that they haven't had in decades."},{"time":959743,"text":"And, partners who were\nsexually indifferent"},{"time":962680,"text":"find themselves suddenly\nso lustfully voracious,"},{"time":965279,"text":"they don't know where it's coming from."},{"time":968568,"text":"Something about the fear\nof loss will rekindle desire,"},{"time":972521,"text":"and make way for an entirely\nnew kind of truth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":978133,"text":"So when an affair is exposed,"},{"time":981004,"text":"what are some of the specific things\nthat couples can do?"},{"time":986133,"text":"We know from trauma that healing begins"},{"time":990204,"text":"when the perpetrator\nacknowledges their wrongdoing."},{"time":995339,"text":"So for the partner who had the affair,"},{"time":999050,"text":"for Nick,"},{"time":1000582,"text":"one thing is to end the affair,"},{"time":1002387,"text":"but the other is the essential,\nimportant act of expressing"},{"time":1007109,"text":"guilt and remorse for hurting his wife."},{"time":1010889,"text":"But the truth is"},{"time":1012264,"text":"that I have noticed that quite a lot\nof people who have affairs"},{"time":1015365,"text":"may feel terribly guilty\nfor hurting their partner,"},{"time":1018463,"text":"but they don't feel guilty\nfor the experience of the affair itself."},{"time":1022135,"text":"And that distinction is important."},{"time":1025230,"text":"And Nick, he needs to hold\nvigil for the relationship."},{"time":1029253,"text":"He needs to become, for a while,\nthe protector of the boundaries."},{"time":1032326,"text":"It's his responsibility to bring it up,"},{"time":1034949,"text":"because if he thinks about it,"},{"time":1036929,"text":"he can relieve Heather from the obsession,"},{"time":1039939,"text":"and from having to make sure\nthat the affair isn't forgotten,"},{"time":1043149,"text":"and that in itself\nbegins to restore trust."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1047570,"text":"But for Heather,"},{"time":1049429,"text":"or deceived partners,"},{"time":1051174,"text":"it is essential to do things\nthat bring back a sense of self-worth,"},{"time":1056512,"text":"to surround oneself with love\nand with friends and activities"},{"time":1060249,"text":"that give back joy\nand meaning and identity."},{"time":1063936,"text":"But even more important,"},{"time":1065869,"text":"is to curb the curiosity\nto mine for the sordid details --"},{"time":1070772,"text":"Where were you? Where did you do it?"},{"time":1072969,"text":"How often? Is she better\nthan me in bed? --"},{"time":1075991,"text":"questions that only inflict more pain,"},{"time":1078475,"text":"and keep you awake at night."},{"time":1080674,"text":"And instead, switch to what I call\nthe investigative questions,"},{"time":1085350,"text":"the ones that mine\nthe meaning and the motives --"},{"time":1088654,"text":"What did this affair mean for you?"},{"time":1091127,"text":"What were you able to express\nor experience there"},{"time":1093899,"text":"that you could no longer do with me?"},{"time":1096154,"text":"What was it like for you\nwhen you came home?"},{"time":1099186,"text":"What is it about us that you value?"},{"time":1102585,"text":"Are you pleased this is over?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1106404,"text":"Every affair will redefine a relationship,"},{"time":1110725,"text":"and every couple will determine"},{"time":1113607,"text":"what the legacy of the affair will be."},{"time":1117649,"text":"But affairs are here to stay,\nand they're not going away."},{"time":1122316,"text":"And the dilemmas of love and desire,"},{"time":1124959,"text":"they don't yield just simple answers\nof black and white and good and bad,"},{"time":1130929,"text":"and victim and perpetrator."},{"time":1134221,"text":"Betrayal in a relationship\ncomes in many forms."},{"time":1138296,"text":"There are many ways\nthat we betray our partner:"},{"time":1140650,"text":"with contempt, with neglect,"},{"time":1142819,"text":"with indifference, with violence."},{"time":1145999,"text":"Sexual betrayal is only\none way to hurt a partner."},{"time":1149437,"text":"In other words, the victim of an affair"},{"time":1152041,"text":"is not always the victim of the marriage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1157840,"text":"Now, you've listened to me,"},{"time":1160048,"text":"and I know what you're thinking:"},{"time":1162423,"text":"She has a French accent,\nshe must be pro-affair."},{"time":1166697,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1171761,"text":"So, you're wrong."},{"time":1173619,"text":"I am not French."},{"time":1175666,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1178143,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":1181602,"text":"And I'm not pro-affair."},{"time":1184674,"text":"But because I think that good\ncan come out of an affair,"},{"time":1189058,"text":"I have often been asked\nthis very strange question:"},{"time":1192413,"text":"Would I ever recommend it?"},{"time":1195514,"text":"Now, I would no more\nrecommend you have an affair"},{"time":1198505,"text":"than I would recommend you have cancer,"},{"time":1201049,"text":"and yet we know that people\nwho have been ill"},{"time":1203752,"text":"often talk about how their illness\nhas yielded them a new perspective."},{"time":1208569,"text":"The main question that I've been asked\nsince I arrived at this conference"},{"time":1211906,"text":"when I said I would talk\nabout infidelity is, for or against?"},{"time":1216488,"text":"I said, \"Yes.\""},{"time":1218162,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1221868,"text":"I look at affairs from a dual perspective:"},{"time":1225505,"text":"hurt and betrayal on one side,"},{"time":1229153,"text":"growth and self-discovery on the other --"},{"time":1232509,"text":"what it did to you,\nand what it meant for me."},{"time":1236621,"text":"And so when a couple comes to me\nin the aftermath of an affair"},{"time":1241289,"text":"that has been revealed,"},{"time":1243092,"text":"I will often tell them this:"},{"time":1245420,"text":"Today in the West,"},{"time":1247825,"text":"most of us are going to have\ntwo or three relationships"},{"time":1252704,"text":"or marriages,"},{"time":1254403,"text":"and some of us are going\nto do it with the same person."},{"time":1258666,"text":"Your first marriage is over."},{"time":1261633,"text":"Would you like to create\na second one together?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1265164,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1266619,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}